{"tid":1835791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【急推！幫還柙手足問！】監房手足，你問我答","createTime":"2020-01-23T03:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T04:00:10.000Z","uid":270466,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9ea1e9293168b2be64b98fe5fd8416eb4e69df97","tid":1835791,"uid":270466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T03:24:07.000Z","msg":"事緣係上次我喺度share咗篇喺蘋果嘅公開信 (寫信嗰個手足自稱做stories behind the prison，後來先知原來佢係我個friend個friend)︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200108/PVXOYKQB5ERAKJJ63AUGDX4BQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200108%2FPVXOYKQB5ERAKJJ63AUGDX4BQY%2F&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=6df16d61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200108%2FPVXOYKQB5ERAKJJ63AUGDX4BQY%2F&h=aad0894b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200108/PVXOYKQB5ERAKJJ63AUGDX4BQY/</a><br />\n<br />\n佢最近再寫信出嚟話想借連登acc出post，因為想繼續寫公開信，同大家講吓監房小故事，又或者係想大家傾下出面嘅嘢，唔想因為還柙而中斷咗同外界嘅聯繫，所以想公開求問大家寫咩題材。信嘅內容如下 (我都會將呢個連登post俾埋張超雄議辦，希望工作人員會幫手出post)︰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yMNOjWp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyMNOjWp.jpg&h=0b62a959&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「巴絲們你地好，我係之前寫咗好長公開信果個手足<br />\n見到你哋嘅留言真係又開心又滾動 (sticker︰連狗喊喊)<br />\n不過叫我兄弟真係好好笑<br />\n<br />\n喺度還柙就嚟悶死我啦，想寫吓啲監房小故事俾大家睇呀<br />\n但因為喺度坐咗一段時間，同出面社會有些少脫節<br />\n又驚寫完啲嘢出嚟唔好睇，或者你哋唔中意睇<br />\n<br />\n所以想收集下大家意見<br />\n你哋有咩想知想八卦就留言啦<br />\n輕鬆 or 沉重嘅主題我都會分享 (sticker︰連豬打鼓x3)<br />\n我會努力寫同努力生活，唔使擔心<br />\n<br />\n同埋見有巴絲問想寄信俾我<br />\n可以寄去張超雄議辦 (立法會道一號立法會綜合大樓1017室張超雄議員辦事處)<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n感性還感性，平日我都係上lecture果陣碌吹水台同cc台嘅災嚟<br />\n想講好掛住6月之前嘅連登<br />\n沒有分化post，只有分手post嘅連登 (sticker︰腦魔喊喊)<br />\n<br />\n我同其他拋緊，坐緊嘅手足都唔會放棄<br />\n你哋都唔可以！<br />\n我哋唔喺度嘅日子你哋要努力啦<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n希望有朝一日我坐完監出嚟仲可以見到你哋<br />\n你哋要保重呀知唔知」"},{"pid":"35e669d81b210d9468419d55a07835fdc1a2141b","tid":1835791,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T03:42:31.000Z","msg":"留名睇"},{"pid":"7f90d9bd633a999ed2959fb5db3f8fde97b7a733","tid":1835791,"uid":134342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T03:55:06.000Z","msg":"名已留"},{"pid":"2957250eb0d38838169e94e33d76fbbc75fed70f","tid":1835791,"uid":66585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T03:56:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"addae1a21249cfd013a525ed935ea6af11b37515","tid":1835791,"uid":105271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T03:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff974dad32e91ae5cec3af49642d868679238717","tid":1835791,"uid":253223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:00:10.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}